              <br><br>
              Some of Justin's must-have products include: Ibiza cork round brushes, Enzo Milano clipless curling irons, J Beverly Hills styling products and Dikson ArgaBeta Oil. 
            </div>
          </div>  

           <div class="bio">
            <div class="name-and-company">Colin Caruso: <a href="http://www.paulmitchell.com/" target="_blank">Paul Mitchell</a></div>
            <div class="text">
